::ai::agent ns
meta {
    doc: """
    Reusable harness primitives for AI agents.

    `hot-ai` owns the low-level `::ai::*` building blocks: chat loops,
    memory, RAG, skills, tools, and inter-agent bus messages. This
    package extends that family with `::ai::agent::*`, the higher-level
    runtime surface that concrete agents can share:

    - `::ai::agent::transport` for normalized transport messages.
    - `::ai::agent::command` for command parsing and declarations.
    - `::ai::agent::runtime` for session registries, stores, stats, and
      error logging.
    - `::ai::agent::render` for neutral reply records and text helpers.
    - `::ai::agent::stream` for agent-level stream event labels and
      emit helpers (a thin wrapper over the engine's `::hot::stream`).
    - `::ai::agent::memory` for reusable memory lifecycle command
      declarations and response shapes (the command-surface sibling
      of `::ai::memory`, which is the memory engine).
    - `::ai::agent::lifecycle` for scheduled memory lifecycle helpers.
    - `::ai::agent::mcp` for common MCP tool plumbing.
    - `::ai::agent::request` for per-request session/identity bindings
      that let statically-registered tools recover the active caller.
    - `::ai::agent::chat-turn` for the canonical memory-grounded LLM
      reply lifecycle (recall → persist user → stream → persist
      assistant) used by free-chat handlers.
    - `::ai::agent::notify` for a runtime-scoped notification ledger so
      scheduled handlers (daily recaps, stale-task nudges, standups)
      have somewhere to land output when no client is listening.
    - `::ai::agent::synthesis` for the one-shot, non-streaming LLM
      pattern that scheduled handlers use to turn a memory window into
      a notification body.
    """
}

AgentRuntime ::ai::agent::runtime/AgentRuntime
IncomingMessage ::ai::agent::transport/IncomingMessage
OutboundMessage ::ai::agent::transport/OutboundMessage
TransportCapabilities ::ai::agent::transport/TransportCapabilities
Command ::ai::agent::command/Command
Reply ::ai::agent::render/Reply
RetentionPolicy ::ai::agent::memory/RetentionPolicy
MemoryInspection ::ai::agent::memory/MemoryInspection
LifecycleJob ::ai::agent::lifecycle/LifecycleJob
Notification ::ai::agent::notify/Notification
SynthesisInput ::ai::agent::synthesis/SynthesisInput
SynthesisResult ::ai::agent::synthesis/SynthesisResult
